{"tid":996783,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"統 計 網 站 分 析 網 紅 明 星 Ig 假 粉 絲","createTime":"2019-01-26T14:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T12:40:52.000Z","uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"63dda740e3cb8ab0abde8fcb81ef6983ed77cf10","tid":996783,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAr39o0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAr39o0.png&h=7f8664e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前陣子剛掀起一陣小風波， 11 月Instagram公布正以 AI 刪除假帳號，進行「大清洗」，要將所有「假帳戶」清走，一度嚇到各位「買followers」的網紅人心惶惶；這天，根據《PhotoblogHK》的報導指出，噗浪網站創辦人之一的 Alvin Woon 早前設計了統計網站「Hot Influencer」，列出市面上最受歡迎 KOL 的各項數據，包括參與率和假粉絲比例。<br />\n <br />\n「Hot Influencer」這個網站現時存有大約 120 萬個擁有一萬或以上追蹤者的網紅統計資料。網站的FAQ指出，其針對某些hashtag不斷like posts、定期間 follow 與 unfollow 帳號，如robot般操作帳號，以及開宗明義寫道提供買賣粉絲服務的宣傳帳戶也被定義為假粉絲。<br />\n <br />\n網站所列出的 Fake Followers 其實只是一個數字，純粹根據一條數字方程式所得出結果，並不代表以上用戶的確有用真金白銀買粉絲，只供各位參考。用戶與用戶之間的百分比有所分別，大家亦可從中自行分析因由；舉例說明，不同用戶的讀者性質有所不一，如 @diet_prada 常以惹起公眾話題的時尚個案作為主要內容，愛與追蹤者進行互動，自然粉絲有經常回應留言於帳戶的動態；如果是主要以「擺pose」分享個人衣櫥的時尚網紅，粉絲們對其內容的反應也有所出入，因此會寫上數據之間的差別，也不一定是因為他們有買粉絲的嫌疑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣研究KOL粉絲數的各位可前往以下網站參詳一下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hotinfluencer.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhotinfluencer.com%2F&d=WN7QTdLR8ps8ZSj%2F63IP5J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7d45161a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hotinfluencer.com/</a>"},{"pid":"9abe945ac9918874d681938161f64f5a08331f46","tid":996783,"uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ln0AB0W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fln0AB0W.jpg&h=20483ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rdEaBrH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrdEaBrH.jpg&h=d8b44426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Sw2Stdz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSw2Stdz.jpg&h=dc1910be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96968fd5076256c1a40932aa06619b1e62bfd5a","tid":996783,"uid":83102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"有冇D乜好出名好多followers但又好小fake followers?"},{"pid":"638e8c894bced4196a3ed38c69e390136bee9dab","tid":996783,"uid":31798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b96968fd5076256c1a40932aa06619b1e62bfd5a","tid":996783,"uid":83102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:58:43.000Z","msg":"有冇D乜好出名好多followers但又好小fake followers?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"阿朗"},{"pid":"8712d64a855392c274eefbe901fb70546f41e277","tid":996783,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T17:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973dc2b0b9a24702229f70a897ea1f454b4e2d40","tid":996783,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9abe945ac9918874d681938161f64f5a08331f46","tid":996783,"uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ln0AB0W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fln0AB0W.jpg&h=20483ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rdEaBrH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrdEaBrH.jpg&h=d8b44426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Sw2Stdz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSw2Stdz.jpg&h=dc1910be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /